Tell me.

153
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:58,180
- You're asking about a beautiful,

154
00:09:58,320 --> 00:09:59,720
long-haired blonde woman?

155
00:10:00,180 --> 00:10:01,880
Oh, that would be Anna.

156
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:03,280
- What?

157
00:10:03,540 --> 00:10:03,940
Anna?

158
00:10:04,820 --> 00:10:06,280
- So that young woman, Anna,

159
