162
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:15,220
Go down this alley. It should be about two blocks down.

163
00:10:15,820 --> 00:10:18,260
She's a very friendly, nice young lady.

164
00:10:18,520 --> 00:10:21,080
She always says hi to me when she sees me.

165
00:10:21,340 --> 00:10:23,260
Anna? Uh-huh.

166
00:10:23,820 --> 00:10:25,400
She's such a nice girl.

167
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:28,540
She always has a warm hello and a smile for me.

168
00:10:28,660 --> 00:10:30,920
What's her apartment number and which floor does she live on?

169
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:32,760
Oh, up there.

170
00:10:33,340 --> 00:10:35,780
