171
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:48,780
So if what the boys told us earlier is true, and it turns out the woman who lives here actually did kidnap Milos, and she happens to be a young blonde lady named Anna, then she just might be the one...

172
00:10:51,620 --> 00:10:58,720
You're right. And if this young blonde woman is the person I think she is, I swear this will end here and now.

173
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:16,780
Looks like we're too late.

174
