178
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:49,980
"Those boys got involved in all this because they were trying to prove my innocence."

179
00:11:50,860 --> 00:11:59,160
"You can't blame yourself for everything. The boys told you that Milos usually walks around the streets of Prague. He's always out there searching for his mother."

180
00:11:59,160 --> 00:12:01,860
