192
00:12:32,980 --> 00:12:38,160
went shopping and left me alone with the baby. My son was in his room taking a nap, and when

193
00:12:38,160 --> 00:12:42,700
I went in to check on him, he was face down and had stopped breathing. I began giving

194
00:12:42,700 --> 00:12:48,460
him CPR right away, and I called the doctor at the same time. I did everything I should

195
00:12:48,460 --> 00:12:53,800
have done to help him. I did it perfectly, but my son died anyway.

196
