202
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:19,100
And then my wife left me.

203
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,800
I have to find MiloÅ¡.

204
00:13:24,740 --> 00:13:27,700
You told me that MiloÅ¡ is the child of a prostitute

