206
00:13:31,400 --> 00:13:31,860
I did.

207
00:13:32,980 --> 00:13:36,120
The blonde woman we're looking for is the person I suspect it is.

208
00:13:36,660 --> 00:13:39,340
I don't think she's going to let Milos live.

209
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:43,060
What's worse, she won't just kill him quickly.

210
00:13:45,660 --> 00:13:48,280
If this turns out to be who I think it is,

211
00:13:48,640 --> 00:13:53,060
