212
00:13:57,680 --> 00:14:00,520
Follow this road. It will take you to Germany.

213
00:14:01,060 --> 00:14:02,300
Will I see my mom?

214
00:14:02,980 --> 00:14:05,580
The chances are good. There's a lively town up ahead.

215
00:14:05,780 --> 00:14:07,320
You think that my mom's up there?

216
00:14:07,920 --> 00:14:11,640
I'm going to wait right here for you. You go ahead on your own.

217
00:14:12,060 --> 00:14:14,080
You'll know who your mother is when you see her,

218
00:14:14,280 --> 00:14:17,720
