241
00:16:00,840 --> 00:16:03,320
- Nothing, no, actually, I know your mom personally.

242
00:16:03,760 --> 00:16:04,100
- What?

243
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:04,860
You do?

244
00:16:05,140 --> 00:16:06,240
Show me where she is.

245
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:07,560
- Well, that's hard to do.

246
00:16:07,960 --> 00:16:09,860
There's so many places she could hide.

247
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:11,320
She could be anyone,

248
00:16:11,960 --> 00:16:13,520
any one of 50 women.

249
00:16:14,520 --> 00:16:15,020
(laughing)

250
00:16:22,080 --> 00:16:23,740
- Oh my God, it's you.

251
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:25,220
My boy.

252
00:16:25,780 --> 00:16:26,620
It's you.

253
00:16:27,200 --> 00:16:27,440
- Huh?

254
00:16:27,740 --> 00:16:28,740
Who are you, lady?

255
00:16:28,740 --> 00:16:30,400
